      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "remindb quickstart — internal notes\n\n# Setup\nInstall the binary, then point your\nagent at the db.\n\n## Steps\n- clone the repo\n- run `make build`\n- copy the .db to your notes dir\n\n## Config\n```bash\nremindb serve --db ./notes.db\n```\n| Flag        | Default   |\n| --db        | memory.db |\n| --transport | stdio     |",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "remindb quickstart — internal notes\n\n# Setup\nInstall the binary, then point your\nagent at the db.\n\n## Steps\n- clone the repo\n- run `make build`\n- copy the .db to your notes dir\n\n## Config\n```bash\nremindb serve --db ./notes.db\n```\n| Flag        | Default   |\n| --db        | memory.db |\n| --transport | stdio     |",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a3",
      "autoResize": true
    },
