      "text": "<h1>Architecture</h1>\n<p>The pipeline is\nparser → store.</p>\n\n<img src=\"diagram.png\"\n     alt=\"pipeline\" />\n\n<knowledge weight=\"2.5\">\n  Setup\n</knowledge>\n\n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\">\n  <circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\"\n          r=\"3\" />\n</svg>",
